&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What&#39;s the Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Customer Success Team Lead is a strategic, hands-on role responsible for managing and guiding a team of Customer Success Managers (CSMs). This position plays a vital role in scaling our customer success function and ensuring top-tier service delivery, with a focus on client retention, growth, and satisfaction. You&#39;ll also foster team development, support strategic initiatives, and help shape the future vision of AssetWatch&#39;s customer success journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is located in the United States.&lt;/p&gt;
